          [hannosch]
        
        1.2.1 - 2010-07-01
        ------------------
        
        - Load the ``cmf.*`` permissions from Products.CMFCore.
          [hannosch]
        
        1.2.0 - 2009-03-04
        ------------------
        
        - Added IRefreshableLockable interface and TTWLockable implementation.
          [davisagli]
        
        - Changed default lock timeout to 10 minutes.
          [davisagli]
        
        1.1.0
        -----
        
        - Clarified license and copyright statements.
          [hannosch]
        
